Sigma Alpha Epsilon (SAE) fraternity at Clemson University in South Carolina has been put on probation for two years . 
  The 'Cripmas' party held last December had white students throwing stereotypical gang symbols while dressed in red and blue bandanas and fake 'thug' tattoos . 
  The party flared up racial tensions on campus . 
  Photos from the party flooded social media and were accompanied by comments such as 'Merry Cri pmas to all and all a hood night'